(9, 'Fahmida Nizam', NULL, 'Md Abdur Rahman Forhad', '2022-04-05', 'This paper argued when 15 years of rotations of Acacia auriculiformis plantation is practiced in the degraded lands in an area of 0.15mha of Chittagong district, the present revenue flow from this plantation will be 326 million US$. The total value is calculated using the international carbon market price US$18/MgC,  using a seven percent interest rate. Also, this plantation will sequestrate a total of 17.07 million Mg carbon. Sensitivity analysis is also done using other rates, such as 9% and 11%. However, the study does not evaluate the net present value.', NULL, 'ESV 67052545', '5', '2022-03-31 09:07:18', '2022-04-05 19:43:12'),
(10, 'Fahmida Nizam', NULL, 'Md Abdur Rahman Forhad', '2022-04-05', 'The study mainly considers tree plantation, privately raised on land leased from the government. Therefore, the study finds trees like Clerodendrum viscosum (bhat), Mimosa pudica (lajjabati), Caealpinia cristael (kootumkanta), Hyptic sauveolens (tokma), Eupatorium odoratum (assamlata), Mikania cordata (tarakanta), and Melastoma melabatricum (tea indicator) with a few vines and creepers. In addition, local people frequently used the plantation for fuel material collection. The study does not evaluate carbon sequestration separately for each tree plantation, horticulture, and grassland program. Additionally, the study does not estimate the net present value.', NULL, 'ESV 93346124', '5', '2022-03-31 09:28:02', '2022-04-05 19:34:10'),
(11, 'Fahmida Nizam', NULL, 'Md Abdur Rahman Forhad', '2022-04-05', 'This paper first analyses the effects of grassland, along with tree plantation and horticulture, on the soil properties in the degraded hills of Chittagong District. This study considered the grassland, established in marshy valleys by the Hathazari Dairy Firm, where three fodder types of grass, viz. Pennisetum typhoidum (napier), Phaselus mungo (maskolai) and Panicum maximum (gini grass) were grown in mixed culture for 9 years. This study estimates the valuation of the carbon sequestration for the three vegetated lands altogether. However, the study does not evaluate the net present value.', NULL, 'ESV 95014258', '5', '2022-03-31 09:46:36', '2022-04-05 19:30:23'),
(12, 'Fahmida Nizam', NULL, 'Md Abdur Rahman Forhad', '2022-04-05', 'This paper first analyses the effects of  horticulture on the soil properties in the degraded hills of Chittagong District. The plantation consisted of fruit trees like Artocarpus heterophyllus (jackfruit), Mangifera indica (mango), Psidium guajava (guava), Manilkara sapota (safeda), Litchi chiensis (litchi) and Zizyphus mauritiana (boroi). This estimates the valuation of the carbon sequestration for three vegetated lands, tree plantation, horticulture, and grassland. However, the study does not evaluate the net present value.', NULL, 'ESV 91414090', '5', '2022-03-31 09:53:44', '2022-04-05 19:26:54'),
(13, 'Md. Seikh Sadiul Islam Tanvir', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ESV 91791033', '5', '2022-03-31 10:09:36', '2022-03-31 10:09:36'),
