(24, 'Aynun Nishat Farhabi', NULL, 'Mohammad Belal Uddin', '2022-04-05', 'Each family is allotted about 2.5-3.0 acres of forest land by the Forest Department. The allotment is demarcated and granted on a renewal basis for 99 years, with the condition that they provide their labor in developing and managing forest plantations. The exact quantity of ecosystem services produced are not mentioned in the paper.', NULL, 'ESV 69288004', '5', '2022-03-31 11:06:13', '2022-04-05 19:10:22'),
(27, 'Umme Honey Haque', NULL, 'Md Sariful Islam', '2022-04-05', 'No valuation has been performed. The quantity data are collected form various literatures.', NULL, 'ESV 38879640', '5', '2022-03-31 15:57:37', '2022-04-05 20:00:39'),
(28, 'Md. Seikh Sadiul Islam Tanvir', NULL, 'Suriya Yeasmin', '2022-04-05', 'The Study is about assesing the benefit of agroforestry over a period of 10 year in the area around Madhupur national park. The farmers mainly grow agricultural crops, fruit crops and timber in the same piece of land. Here how much monetary value is originated by the individual product is not quantified. They have calculated the total cost and benefits over 10 years. The quantities of timber and crops are also not mentioned.', NULL, 'ESV 56655311', '5', '2022-03-31 16:08:03', '2022-04-05 18:34:05'),
(29, 'Aynun Nishat Farhabi', NULL, 'Mohammad Belal Uddin', '2022-04-05', NULL, NULL, 'ESV 56562372', '5', '2022-03-31 16:16:53', '2022-04-05 18:23:30'),
(30, 'Aynun Nishat Farhabi', NULL, 'Mohammad Belal Uddin', '2022-04-05', 'The calculated value of annual tangible production per hectare was US$535.2 with and US$674.9 without family labor cost.', NULL, 'ESV 38300298', '5', '2022-03-31 17:10:52', '2022-04-05 18:21:13'),
(31, 'Shakhera Akter Shimu', NULL, 'Md Golam Rakkibu', '2022-04-05', 'Valuation has not been performed in this paper. The physical properties of soil on two hill slopes of 35% and 55% in orange orchard cultivated by the Mro tribe of Chittagong \r\nHill Tracts (CHTs) were evaluated and compared with those of bushy hill forests. This paper is essential for policy making whether the land use can be changed or not seeing the results of different soil properties from different areas.', NULL, 'ESV 36171174', '5', '2022-03-31 21:19:18', '2022-04-05 18:00:35'),
(32, 'Shakhera Akter Shimu', NULL, 'Md Golam Rakkibu', '2022-04-05', 'Valuation has not been performed in this paper. This paper is mainly based on biomass fuel use, burning technique and reasons\r\nfor the denial of improved cooking stoves by Forest User Groups of Rema-Kalenga Wildlife Sanctuary, Bangladesh.', NULL, 'ESV 46981346', '5', '2022-03-31 22:26:05', '2022-04-05 17:53:53'),
