(42, 'Aynun Nishat Farhabi', NULL, 'Mohammad Belal Uddin', '2022-04-05', 'This study has focused on farmers engaged in shrimp production along with other fish species. The average total cost of fish production was BDT 69,112 per acre.', NULL, 'ESV 97937125', '5', '2022-04-02 07:56:16', '2022-04-05 11:34:56'),
(43, 'Shakhera Akter Shimu', NULL, 'Md Golam Rakkibu', '2022-04-04', 'This paper showed the fruitfulness of co-management practice in Rema-Kalenga Wildlife sanctuary including the forest dependency of the surrounding people either their attachment to co-management approach or not. Also mentioned the factors which lead to the selection process for co-management team.  This paper did not mention the amount of fuel wood and grass that come from forest by household. This  paper also did not mention about any other resources that come from forest which show the dependency of the peoples.', NULL, 'ESV 46228113', '5', '2022-04-02 08:12:17', '2022-04-05 11:06:38'),
(44, 'Shakhera Akter Shimu', NULL, 'Md Golam Rakkibu', '2022-04-04', NULL, NULL, 'ESV 17006582', '5', '2022-04-02 08:19:56', '2022-04-05 11:02:09'),
(45, 'Shakhera Akter Shimu', NULL, 'Md Golam Rakkibu', '2022-04-04', 'Using GIS total land accretion rate has been identified. This paper does not have any valuation information. The analyses strongly indicate that mangrove plantations in Bangladesh have contributed to coastal land stabilization and erosion control, an important ecosystem service in light of expected SLR and increased intensity of tropical storm surges due to climate change. The results suggest that, compared to unplanted areas, mangrove plantations have promoted accretion while mitigating erosion in coastal Bangladesh.', NULL, 'ESV 18803248', '5', '2022-04-02 08:25:42', '2022-04-05 10:49:23'),
(46, 'Shakhera Akter Shimu', NULL, 'Md Golam Rakkibu', '2022-04-04', 'The paper did not estimate the monetary value of ecosystem services.', NULL, 'ESV 93298835', '5', '2022-04-02 08:33:18', '2022-04-05 10:14:09'),
(47, 'Compass User', NULL, 'Naeema Jihan Zinia', '2022-04-04', 'The tourism calculation was done based on TCM, which might not be an appropriate method for this study area.', NULL, 'ESV 79201401', '5', '2022-04-02 11:37:43', '2022-04-05 09:39:43'),
(48, 'Compass User', NULL, 'Naeema Jihan Zinia', '2022-04-04', 'The value of biodiversity in BDNP based on the assumptions\r\nof Rousser and Small (2000).', NULL, 'ESV 50721959', '5', '2022-04-02 11:58:35', '2022-04-05 09:35:21'),
(49, 'Md. Seikh Sadiul Islam Tanvir', NULL, 'Suriya Yeasmin', '2022-04-04', NULL, NULL, 'ESV 98203357', '5', '2022-04-02 12:10:26', '2022-04-05 09:32:06'),
(50, 'Umme Honey Haque', NULL, 'Md Abdur Rahman Forhad', '2022-04-04', 'This paper is prepared based on the Bangladesh Forest Inventory (BFI) report. Detailed data for ecosystem sub-services for each forest zone are available with the reference: GoB (2019), Tree and forest resources of Bangladesh: Report on the Bangladesh Forest Inventory. Forest\r\nDepartment, Ministry of Environment, Forest and Climate Change, Government of the People’s Republic\r\nof Bangladesh, Dhaka, Bangladesh.', NULL, 'ESV 83368049', '5', '2022-04-02 15:52:37', '2022-04-05 09:18:08'),
(51, 'Fahmida Nizam', NULL, 'Md Abdur Rahman Forhad', '2022-04-04', NULL, NULL, 'ESV 91564600', '5', '2022-04-02 16:16:21', '2022-04-04 19:12:37'),
(52, 'Fahmida Nizam', NULL, 'Md Abdur Rahman Forhad', '2022-04-04', NULL, NULL, 'ESV 43083499', '5', '2022-04-02 16:22:10', '2022-04-04 19:09:47'),
(53, 'Fahmida Nizam', NULL, 'Md Abdur Rahman Forhad', '2022-04-04', 'Similar to other ecosystem services, Sundarbans offers provisioning services. Using the Department of Forest data, the study estimated the revenue of the provisioning services was 251868 USD in 2001-2002. The study also estimated the same values for 2014-2015. The results show the difference in values between the two periods. Additionally, the study estimated the revenues for the cultural services in both periods. The study also estimated provisioning and cultural forest products in both periods.', NULL, 'ESV 71152477', '5', '2022-04-02 16:39:37', '2022-04-04 19:05:53'),
(54, 'Fahmida Nizam', NULL, 'Md Abdur Rahman Forhad', '2022-04-04', 'Similar to other ecosystem services, Sundarbans offers provisioning services. Using the Department of Forest data, the study estimated the revenue of the provisioning services was 502522 USD in 2014-2015. The study also estimated the same values for 2001-2002. The results show the difference in values between the two periods. Additionally, the study estimated the revenues for the cultural services in both periods.The study also estimated provisioning and cultural forest products in both periods.', NULL, 'ESV 32310061', '5', '2022-04-02 17:04:23', '2022-04-04 18:55:49'),
(55, 'Tahmid Ferdous', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ESV 89599559', '5', '2022-04-02 21:35:32', '2022-04-02 21:35:32'),
(56, 'Fahmida Nizam', NULL, 'Md Abdur Rahman Forhad', '2022-04-04', 'The CMAS is a plot of swampy lands, where mangrove species, such as Golpata, goran, keora, baen, passur, and hargoza, are planted and different fish, such as shrimp, crabs, telapia, perse, tengra, vetki, and amadi, are cultured. The mangrove species are used for other purposes such as follows: 1) Goalpata used for house roofing, fencing, basket, bags, firewood, rope, edible fruits, hat, mat, rain coat, alcohol, medicinal use (Vermicide, analgesic), Fishing, transport fuel; 2) Keora used for the cot, fuelwood, showcase, chair, fencing, table, roofing, ceiling, and house column; 3) Hargoza used for fuelwood; 4) Possur used for the cot, almirah, ahowcase, aeiling, house column, chair, table, and roofing; and finally, 5) Baen used for fencing, box, roofing, cot, and fuelwood.', NULL, 'ESV 42497199', '5', '2022-04-03 03:22:43', '2022-04-04 18:36:55'),
