(63, 'Aynun Nishat Farhabi', NULL, 'Mohammad Belal Uddin', '2022-04-04', 'The total household members in the 47 sampled households\r\nwere 238. Products, productivity (kg), market value (Tk.) and earnings (Tk.) per household from jhum in a year according\r\nto three landholding classes are assessed in this paper.', NULL, 'ESV 79451300', '5', '2022-04-03 11:03:37', '2022-04-04 17:46:53'),
(64, 'Aynun Nishat Farhabi', NULL, 'Mohammad Belal Uddin', '2022-04-04', 'No specific description of the produced products (quantity) are available. Only names of the agroforestry systems, marketable products, market values, total costs and net incomes are given.', NULL, 'ESV 77457456', '5', '2022-04-03 11:40:50', '2022-04-04 17:05:18'),
(65, 'Aynun Nishat Farhabi', NULL, 'Mohammad Belal Uddin', '2022-04-04', 'On average, the regeneration rate on the CWS forest floor was\r\n77,028 seedlings per ha in 2012. The regeneration rate in 142\r\nsample plots across the CWS reached an average of 83,520\r\nseedlings per ha in 2015. This translates into a net increase in\r\nnatural regeneration rate of 8.43%.', NULL, 'ESV 40725582', '5', '2022-04-03 11:48:02', '2022-04-04 15:18:40'),
(67, 'Umme Honey Haque', NULL, 'Md Sariful Islam', '2022-04-04', NULL, NULL, 'ESV 22867145', '5', '2022-04-03 12:03:29', '2022-04-04 13:09:52'),
(68, 'Aynun Nishat Farhabi', NULL, 'Mohammad Belal Uddin', '2022-04-04', NULL, NULL, 'ESV 74683885', '5', '2022-04-03 12:11:11', '2022-04-04 13:43:07'),
